long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Auto Apply Ai applies to hundreds of jobs a day on LinkedIn using easy apply. Auto filling the application for you and saving all questions asked. 

Regardless of what job you want to apply for this tool will auto apply to jobs for you continuously. We have a delay between each automation done, so it looks like a human is actually going it. 

If you are looking for a free tool to apply to jobs on LinkedIn you’re in the right place. -> This is completely free and there is no upgrade or any kind of charge and effortlessly integrates with LinkedIn.    

Get Started:  
1. Click "Add to Chrome".
2. Log in to LinkedIn and you will see the easy apply button. 
3. Click Run Easy Apply and it will ask to navigate to the job search page if you are not there already. 
4. You need to fill out default values before you start, to train the ai with basic information, like name, email, desired salary, location.
5. Filter for the desired job you want and then click Run Auto Apply. 
6. It will apply to jobs and save every question that the job asks you, as well as the amount of times the question is asked.  
7. You can go to the Form Control page by clicking the plugin and selecting Form Control. Here you can change any answers for the questions for future use.  

Advanced Features like:
* Form Control
* Question Counter
* Built in Ai

For more information on how Auto Apply Ai extension works take a look at https://multipleremotejobs.com/pages/plugin and enjoy seamless Job Applying.
 If you have any problems or feedback regarding Auto Apply Ai extension, write to us at multipleremotejobs@gmail.com, we have a 3-5 day turn around for any errors or bugs.
